acceptRentalOffer(address,uint256,uint25.notice: here the owner of the NFT accepts the rental of the NFT. The rental price is transfered to owner and the syntethic is minted to buyer.

listOffer(address,uint256,uint256,uint25.notice: this is the owner listing his NFT for rental. If the collection is new, mints a new rentalSyntheticNFT contract.

rentalOffer(address,uint256,uint256,uint.notice: this is a person trying to renti an NFT. He/She gets a synthetic NFT linking to the rental manager which registered this new syntheticNFT and set in status active till the date of invalidating it. The buyer pays the rental in advance.
